/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\/#Steps_to_become_a_Lab-Scientist\" title=\"Steps to become a Lab-Scientist\">Steps to become a Lab-Scientist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\/#Medical_Laboratory_Technologist\" title=\"Medical Laboratory Technologist\">Medical Laboratory Technologist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\/#Estimated_Salary_How_to_Become_a_Med_Lab-scientist\" title=\"Estimated Salary| How to Become a Med Lab-scientist\">Estimated Salary| How to Become a Med Lab-scientist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\/#Basic_Skill_Required\" title=\"Basic Skill Required\">Basic Skill Required<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\/#Jobs_in_Med_Laboratory\" title=\"Jobs in Med Laboratory\">Jobs in Med Laboratory<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\/#Education_needed_in_Laboratory\" title=\"Education needed in Laboratory\">Education needed in Laboratory<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\/#Subject_in_Laboratory_How_to_Become_a_Med_Lab-scientist\" title=\"Subject in Laboratory| How to Become a Med Lab-scientist\">Subject in Laboratory| How to Become a Med Lab-scientist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\/#Job_in_crime_MLT_How_to_Become_a_Med_Lab-scientist\" title=\"Job in crime MLT| How to Become a Med Lab-scientist\">Job in crime MLT| How to Become a Med Lab-scientist<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><em><strong>Medical Laboratory Scientist employment has a good outlook because it is a vital part of Canada\u2019s healthcare system read more and learn more below.<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82536336\">Steps to become a Lab-Scientist<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82536337\">Medical Laboratory Technologist<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82536338\">Estimated Salary<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82536339\">Basic Skill Required<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82536340\">Jobs in Med Laboratory<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82536341\">Education needed in Laboratory<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82536342\">Subject in Laboratory<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82536343\">Job in crime MLT<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"steps-to-become-a-lab-scientist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Steps_to_become_a_Lab-Scientist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82536336\"><\/a>Steps to become a Lab-Scientist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>To become an MLT you must first:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Find entry-level work<\/li>\n<li>Earn at least ASCP certification<\/li>\n<li>Get a high school diploma<\/li>\n<li>Gain a clinical experience<\/li>\n<li>Have a bachelor\u2019s degree.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"medical-laboratory-technologist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Medical_Laboratory_Technologist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82536337\"><\/a>Medical Laboratory Technologist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>It is a regulated profession in all Canadian provinces except for British Columbia Prince Edward Island (PEI), and the Territories.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"estimated-salary-how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Estimated_Salary_How_to_Become_a_Med_Lab-scientist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82536338\"><\/a>Estimated Salary| How to Become a Med Lab-scientist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The average salary of MLT in Canada is $45,495 per year or $23.33 per hour<\/li>\n<li>Entry-level positions start at $34,938 per year and $60,408 per year.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"basic-skill-required\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Basic_Skill_Required\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82536339\"><\/a>Basic Skill Required<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Knowledge of chemistry including the safe use and disposal of chemicals.<\/li>\n<li>Knowledge of biology.<\/li>\n<li>The ability to work well with your hands.<\/li>\n<li>To be thorough and pay attention to detail.<\/li>\n<li>The ability to use your initiative.<\/li>\n<li>The ability to work well with others.<\/li>\n<li>Administration skills.<\/li>\n<li>Maths knowledge.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"jobs-in-med-laboratory\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Jobs_in_Med_Laboratory\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82536340\"><\/a>Jobs in Med Laboratory<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>There are many types of laboratory professionals, including<\/strong><strong>:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Medical Laboratory Scientists.<\/li>\n<li>Medical Laboratory Technicians.<\/li>\n<li>Cytotechnologist<\/li>\n<li>Phlemotogists<\/li>\n<li>Histotechnologists<\/li>\n<li>Molecular Biologists.<\/li>\n<li>Pathologists&#8217; Assistants.<\/li>\n<li>Clinical Chemists.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"education-needed-in-laboratory\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Education_needed_in_Laboratory\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82536341\"><\/a>Education needed in Laboratory<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Lab technicians need at minimum a high school diploma or equivalent to work. Most companies prefer at least an Associate&#8217;s Degree in Laboratory Science or a related major. It can be helpful to earn a degree from an institution accredited by the National Accrediting Agency for Clinical Laboratory Sciences.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"subject-in-laboratory-how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Subject_in_Laboratory_How_to_Become_a_Med_Lab-scientist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82536342\"><\/a>Subject in Laboratory| How to Become a Med Lab-scientist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Health Education and Health Communication.<\/li>\n<li>Human Anatomy.<\/li>\n<li>Human Physiology.<\/li>\n<li>PC Software Lab.<\/li>\n<li>Bio-Medical Waste Management.<\/li>\n<li>Communication Lab.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"job-in-crime-mlt-how-to-become-a-med-lab-scientist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Job_in_crime_MLT_How_to_Become_a_Med_Lab-scientist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82536343\"><\/a>Job in crime MLT| How to Become a Med Lab-scientist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>Jobs directly related to your degree include:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Analytical chemist.<\/li>\n<li>Biomedical scientist.<\/li>\n<li>Crime scene investigator.<\/li>\n<li>Forensic scientist.<\/li>\n<li>Scientific laboratory technician.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>See also &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; <a title=\"THE CRYPTO BULL MARKET TO RISE AGAIN ON JULY\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/the-crypto-bull-market-to-rise-again-on-july\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">THE CRYPTO BULL MARKET TO RISE AGAIN ON JULY<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"How to Become a Med Lab-scientist, Medical Laboratory Technologist, Basic salary, basic sk